data.description: Welcome to your dream home, this charming property boasts an impressive array of features. With 4 bedrooms all conveniently located on one level, this home ensures comfort and privacy for everyone in the family. The property also offers extra living space upstairs, perfect for a home office, playroom, or additional lounge area. Both bathrooms have recently undergone renovations, showcasing modern fixtures and sleek designs, prioritizing comfort and style. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, you get the best of both worlds with a peaceful ambiance and easy access to local amenities.
